Description: Python package installer (pip)
 pip, the PyPA recommended tool for installing Python packages, built from the
 upstream pip wheel. Shipped independently of CPython so pip can be updated on
 its own release cadence without rebuilding interpreters.

Package: python3-pip-whl
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Python package installer (pip wheel)
 The pip wheel package for use by ensurepip to bootstrap pip inside virtual
 environments created with python3 -m venv.
